<i>on the floor ♪</i>

13:30.310 --> 13:32.813
‐ Oh, Sylvester. Nice.
‐ Who?

13:33.438 --> 13:34.690
‐ The song. It's Sylvester.

13:36.108 --> 13:37.442
‐ This is not a woman singing?

13:37.442 --> 13:38.569
‐ No.

13:39.278 --> 13:42.406
Not technically... but in some way, kinda.

13:43.031 --> 13:44.825
