16:07.301 --> 16:09.052
Okay. Number four on the list:

16:09.052 --> 16:10.053
Timothy Marshall.

16:11.305 --> 16:12.806
I'm just kidding. It's Ben.

16:13.182 --> 16:14.558
Of course it's fucking Ben.

16:17.519 --> 16:19.354
<i>I mean, there are a few things</i>
<i>more awkward in life</i>

16:19.354 --> 16:22.482
<i>than not having the...</i>
<i>"I love you" returned.</i>

16:22.983 --> 16:24.443
<i>But I wasn't ready to give up.</i>

16:24.818 --> 16:26.486
<i>No, I was too afraid to. And then...</i>

16:27.446 --> 16:29.072
<i>one day, he said it, too.</i>

16:32.701 --> 16:33.702
What?

16:34.578 --> 16:36.788
‐ Just thinking how great it is
to see your face

16:37.664 --> 16:39.249
and how much I love you.

16:40.751 --> 16:41.752
‐ Say it again.

16:41.752 --> 16:43.170
<i>I was happy.</i>

16:43.170 --> 16:44.546
<i>And I thought he loved me for me.</i>

16:44.546 --> 16:45.506
‐ I love you.

16:47.216 --> 16:49.176
SIMON: <i>I wish I'd known</i>
<i>it wasn't gonna last.</i>

16:49.176 --> 16:51.512
‐ I love you.
I love you.

16:51.929 --> 16:53.514
SIMON:
<i>I would've enjoyed it more.</i>

16:53.514 --> 16:54.765
Good.

16:54.765 --> 16:55.933
And I love you, too.

16:57.309 --> 16:58.685
‐ You wanna grab breakfast somewhere?

16:59.019 --> 17:00.938
‐ No, I can't.
I have to go open the store.

17:00.938 --> 17:03.148
‐ Again? Does Rob even work there anymore?

17:03.148 --> 17:04.316
‐ Oh, give her a break.

17:05.192 --> 17:07.945
