17:55.659 --> 17:56.743
‐ Move in with me.

17:58.537 --> 17:59.705
‐ What?

17:59.705 --> 18:01.123
‐ You won't have to worry about rent,

18:01.123 --> 18:04.334
and you can... quit your job
and go back to school

18:04.334 --> 18:06.044
or find your passion, whatever that is.

18:06.753 --> 18:08.005
I just want you to be happy.

18:09.298 --> 18:10.424
‐ I am happy.

18:11.008 --> 18:13.051
‐No, I‐‐ You know what I mean.

18:14.761 --> 18:17.139
Well, just promise me
you'll think about it?

18:18.056 --> 18:19.016
‐ Yeah.

18:19.766 --> 18:20.934
Yeah, sure.

18:20.934 --> 18:22.227
[cell phone buzzes]

18:24.771 --> 18:25.772
What the fuck?

18:27.649 --> 18:28.692
Sam?

18:33.906 --> 18:35.282
‐ I'll see you tonight, baby.
‐ Yeah.

18:36.867 --> 18:38.493
SIMON:
<i>See, I'd finally figured it out.</i>

18:39.369 --> 18:41.455
<i>The thing that was holding us back</i>
<i>this whole time.</i>

18:42.456 --> 18:44.458
<i>Ben was embarrassed by me.</i>

18:45.000 --> 18:46.251
<i>Also, though:</i>

18:46.251 --> 18:47.794
Who the fuck is Sam?

18:50.756 --> 18:51.757
‐ Everybody listen up.

18:52.758 --> 18:55.010
Let's hear it for the newest

18:55.010 --> 18:57.429
and, let's face it, best dressed

18:57.888 --> 18:59.890
partner at Reingold, Smith, and Smith,

18:59.890 --> 19:01.266
Benjamin Young.

19:01.266 --> 19:04.520
[all cheering]

19:04.978 --> 19:08.857
‐ Thank you! Uh, I couldn't have done it
without the help of me and only me.

19:08.857 --> 19:09.775
[laughter]

19:10.901 --> 19:12.861
MAN: Congratulations
‐ Thank you. Thank you so much.

19:12.861 --> 19:13.862
Thank you.

19:14.947 --> 19:19.451
[indiscernible conversations]

19:20.994 --> 19:22.663
BENJAMIN:
Claudia, thank you so much.

