20:40.157 --> 20:42.201
Fuck off! Go mingle, "hotstuff"!

20:43.493 --> 20:44.494
‐ "Sam"?

20:44.494 --> 20:46.580
‐ Yeah, I saw
your flirty little text with him.

20:46.580 --> 20:48.540
<i>I really wanted to trust Ben‐‐</i>

20:48.540 --> 20:49.708
‐ You went through my phone?

20:49.708 --> 20:51.001
‐ [mockingly]
You went through my phone?

20:51.418 --> 20:53.337
