22:45.657 --> 22:46.658
‐ Uh‐huh.

22:47.451 --> 22:48.702
‐ It's been a while.

22:50.162 --> 22:51.663
‐ It has. It's been about a year.

22:52.539 --> 22:53.790
‐ Yeah, wow, a year.

22:56.418 --> 22:57.586
