with you some time.

23:26.406 --> 23:27.783
Maybe grab a drink?

23:28.075 --> 23:29.493
SIMON:
<i>And there he was,</i>

23:29.493 --> 23:32.371
<i>standing right in front of me,</i>
<i>saying everything I ever wanted to hear.</i>

23:32.371 --> 23:34.248
[inaudible]

23:34.248 --> 23:36.375
<i>And I realized if I wanted</i>
<i>a shot at being happy,</i>

23:36.375 --> 23:37.626
<i>I'd have to take a risk‐‐</i>

23:37.626 --> 23:39.920
[horn honking]
‐ Five stars for you, my friend.

23:40.587 --> 23:41.713
‐ Yeah, man, you too.

23:42.339 --> 23:45.551
<i>And Ben just wasn't the risk</i>
